title: GET_WATER_QUAD_BOUNDS
content:
0x42E9A06A// GetWaterQuadBounds
BOOL GET_WATER_QUAD_BOUNDS(int waterQuad, int* minX, int* minY, int* maxX, int* maxY);Parameters:waterQuad: The water quad indexminX: The minX coordinateminY: The minY coordinatemaxX: The maxX coordinatemaxY: The maxY coordinateReturns: Returns true on success. Bounds are undefined on failureExamples:Lualocal success, minX, minY, maxX, maxY = GetWaterQuadBounds(1)
